- Add 'make release' support.


== make release
- yaml.load 'Changes'
- Look at top entry
- Should look like:
    version: 0.12
    date:    
    changes: ...
- This means ready for release.
- Make sure the version # in Changes $PM and git tag look right.
- Fill in the date in Changes file
- perl Makefile.PL
- make test
- sudo make install
- make manifest
- make upload
- make purge
- gciam $VERSION
- git tag $VERSION
- git push
- git push --tags
- check git status
- print summary :)
